            <div id="dsq-comment-message-191" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Ideas can be proved false, but they can never be proved to be true. A natural law can only be said to have not yet been contradicted. 1+1 has always equaled 2, up to today, but there is no guarantee it will equal 2 tomorrow.</p>
