    <li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="dsq-comment-159">
        <div id="dsq-comment-header-159" class="dsq-comment-header">
            <cite id="dsq-cite-159">
http://twitter.com/shrinipedia                <span id="dsq-author-user-159">Aztec Warrior</span>
            </cite>
        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-159" class="dsq-comment-body">
