            <div id="dsq-comment-message-208" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>I would argue that humility and and an ability to check yourself against self-deception to be integral components of Common Sense.  People with common sense tend to be hard to scam and that includes scam themselves thru wishful thinking.</p>
